 467:Drivers/lvgl/src/widgets/bar/lv_bar.c ****      * The drawing direction of the bar can be reversed only when one of the two conditions(value i
 468:Drivers/lvgl/src/widgets/bar/lv_bar.c ****      * or horizontal direction base dir is LV_BASE_DIR_RTL) is met.
 469:Drivers/lvgl/src/widgets/bar/lv_bar.c ****     */
